    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-gray-900 mb-6">🌟 Resources for Volunteers</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Thank you for volunteering your time and energy to support the 2025 DLF Forum! Volunteers are essential to creating a welcoming, inclusive, and well-organized event. Below you’ll find important information to help you prepare for your role.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">📝 Volunteer Roles & Responsibilities</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Volunteers may assist with a range of tasks, including:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6">
      <li>Session monitoring and timekeeping</li>
      <li>Helping attendees navigate the venue</li>
      <li>Supporting registration and check-in</li>
      <li>Distributing programs and materials</li>
      <li>Assisting with accessibility accommodations</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      You’ll receive your role assignment and schedule by email prior to the event. If you have questions about your role or need to request changes, please contact us at <a href="mailto:forum@diglib.org" class="underline text-blue-700">forum@diglib.org</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">🎤 Session Support</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Volunteers assigned to sessions will help with timekeeping, introductions (optional), and reporting issues (e.g. tech problems, accessibility needs). A quick volunteer orientation will be provided onsite to walk you through expectations.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">📍 Checking In</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Please check in at the registration desk when you arrive at the conference venue. A volunteer coordinator will provide you with your badge, a lanyard, and any additional materials you’ll need.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">💬 Questions?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
      We’re here to help! If you have any questions about volunteering, reach out to us at <a href="mailto:forum@diglib.org" class="underline text-blue-700">forum@diglib.org</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
